'''皇家资产管理局''' ([[泰语|Thai]]: สำนักงานทรัพย์สินส่วนพระมหากษัตริย์，英语：Crown Property Bureau，简称CPB) 是[[泰国|泰国]]负责管理皇室财产的准政府机构。<ref>{{cite news|title=Thailand's Royal Wealth|url=http://www.asiasentinel.com/econ-business/thailands-royal-wealth/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=403&Itemid=32|accessdate=19 February 2017|work=Asia Sentinel|date=2007-03-01}}{{Dead link|date=2020年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>该管理局法定为[[法人|法人]]而非政府机构，享有免税的权利。<ref name="NAR-20170821">{{cite news|last1=Ono|first1=Yukako|title=Thai crown holdings at center of Bangkok redevelopment blitz|url=https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics-Economy/Economy/Thai-crown-holdings-at-center-of-Bangkok-redevelopment-blitz?page=2|accessdate=25 August 2017|work=Nikkei Asian Review|date=2017-08-21|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825234157/https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics-Economy/Economy/Thai-crown-holdings-at-center-of-Bangkok-redevelopment-blitz?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref> 据称皇家资产并不属于国王私人所有，而是随着王位传承所有权。<ref name=Grossman>{{cite book|editor1-last=Grossman|editor1-first=Nicholas|editor2-last=Faulder|editor2-first=Dominic|title=King Bhumibol Adulyadej: A Life's Work|date=2012|publisher=Editions Didier Millet|isbn=9814260568|edition=Reprinted}}<!--|accessdate=26 Feb 2015--></ref>{{rp|282}}<ref>[http://www.crownproperty.or.th/history.php Short history from the Crown Property Bureau website] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809000000/http://www.crownproperty.or.th/history.php |date=August 9, 2007 }}</ref>

